  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Rectus re-approximation and periton closure are not the obligatory steps during cesarean
      section. These steps are due to surgeon's preference. However, there is lack of knowledge
      about the relation of rectus muscle re-approximation and adhesion formation. We are going to
      study the rectus muscle stiffness by share-wave elastosonography.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
